metadata.name: THE OG
metadata.description: Get ready to blast off to burger heaven with our OG burger. This juicy beef patty is cooked to perfection and is topped with a trippy blend of melted cheese, psychedelic pickles, and cosmic secret sauce, all served on a groovy sesame seed bun. Ready to be enjoyed or to be burned. Burning 10 OG's will give you 1 Inferno. Go to [cheeseburners.com/ogburn](https://cheeseburners.com/ogburn) to get your burn on 🔥
